---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Insights | ARM Management"
  description="Regulatory updates, jurisdiction guides, and market intelligence from the ARM advisory team — written for operators who need accurate, actionable information across the jurisdictions we serve."
>
<main>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero__bg" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1456324504439-367cee3b3c32?w=1600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__content container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Intelligence</span>
      <h1>Intelligence for<br>International Business.</h1>
      <p>Regulatory updates, jurisdiction guides, and market intelligence — written for operators who need accurate, actionable information.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">About This Publication</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">Written by Practitioners. For Operators.</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">ARM Management publishes regulatory updates, jurisdiction guides, and market intelligence — written by the ARM advisory team for operators who need accurate, actionable information across the jurisdictions we serve.</p>
      <p class="reveal" style="margin-top:20px">Unlike generic business publications, our intelligence is written by advisors who are actively working across these markets — advising on entity formations, licence applications, and cross-border transactions. The information we publish reflects current reality on the ground, not summaries of official publications.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--warm" style="border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Topics We Cover</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">What We Write About</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top:40px">
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <h3>Regulatory Updates</h3>
          <p>Changes to corporate law, tax regimes, employment rules, and licensing requirements across all jurisdictions ARM Management operates in — explained plainly, with the commercial implications highlighted.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <h3>Jurisdiction Guides</h3>
          <p>Practical guides to operating in specific markets: what entity types are available, what compliance obligations arise, what the realistic timeline and cost looks like, and what the common mistakes are.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <h3>Transaction Intelligence</h3>
          <p>Market commentary on cross-border M&amp;A activity, private investment trends, and deal structuring developments across the EU, GCC, Asia Pacific, and Latin America.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <h3>Crypto &amp; Web3 Regulation</h3>
          <p>Updates on VARA, MiCA, MAS, and other virtual asset regulatory frameworks — tracking licence approvals, enforcement actions, and regulatory guidance as it is issued.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <h3>Global Mobility</h3>
          <p>Changes to investor visa and golden visa programmes across the UAE, EU, and Asia — including new programmes, requirement changes, and processing time updates.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <h3>Tax &amp; Compliance</h3>
          <p>Cross-border tax developments, transfer pricing updates, VAT changes, and compliance deadline reminders across the jurisdictions our clients operate in.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Latest Guides</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">Published Intelligence</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top:40px">
        <a class="card reveal" href="/insights/uae-corporate-tax-vat" style="display:block;text-decoration:none">
          <span class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:14px">Tax &amp; Compliance</span>
          <h3>UAE Corporate Tax &amp; VAT</h3>
          <p>The 9% rate and AED 375,000 threshold, free-zone QFZP rules, the 5% VAT and registration thresholds — against official Federal Tax Authority sources.</p>
          <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold)">Read →</span>
        </a>
        <a class="card reveal reveal-delay-1" href="/insights/uae-company-formation" style="display:block;text-decoration:none">
          <span class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:14px">Jurisdiction Guide</span>
          <h3>UAE Company Formation</h3>
          <p>Mainland, free-zone and offshore compared — 100% foreign ownership, licence types, entity structures and the setup process.</p>
          <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold)">Read →</span>
        </a>
        <a class="card reveal reveal-delay-2" href="/insights/uae-golden-visa" style="display:block;text-decoration:none">
          <span class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:14px">Global Mobility</span>
          <h3>The UAE Golden Visa</h3>
          <p>Ten-year residency routes, current thresholds (AED 2M and the AED 30k salaried route), family sponsorship and the application process.</p>
          <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold)">Read →</span>
        </a>
        <a class="card reveal" href="/insights/vara-licence-dubai" style="display:block;text-decoration:none">
          <span class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:14px">Crypto &amp; Web3</span>
          <h3>The VARA Licence in Dubai</h3>
          <p>The seven regulated virtual-asset activities, the two-stage VASP process, the DIFC carve-out and capital requirements.</p>
          <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold)">Read →</span>
        </a>
        <a class="card reveal reveal-delay-1" href="/insights/mica-regulation" style="display:block;text-decoration:none">
          <span class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:14px">Crypto &amp; Web3</span>
          <h3>MiCA: The EU Crypto Rulebook</h3>
          <p>CASP authorisation, the own-funds classes, ESMA passporting — and the transitional period that expires 1 July 2026.</p>
          <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold)">Read →</span>
        </a>
        <a class="card reveal reveal-delay-2" href="/insights/uae-employment-payroll" style="display:block;text-decoration:none">
          <span class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:14px">Payroll &amp; HR</span>
          <h3>UAE Employment &amp; Payroll</h3>
          <p>End-of-service gratuity, the Wage Protection System, the 2026 salary-date rule, Emiratisation and leave entitlements.</p>
          <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold)">Read →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream" style="border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">International Jurisdictions</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">Company Formation &amp; Tax by Country</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal" style="max-width:640px">Practical, verified overviews of how to incorporate and what you'll pay — entity types, corporate tax, VAT and the regimes that matter — across the markets ARM advises in.</p>
      <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top:40px">
        <a class="card reveal" href="/insights/germany-company-formation" style="display:block;text-decoration:none">
          <span class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:14px">Germany</span>
          <h3>Germany</h3>
          <p>The GmbH and UG, the three-part corporate tax stack (~30% combined) and 19% VAT.</p>
          <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold)">Read →</span>
        </a>
        <a class="card reveal reveal-delay-1" href="/insights/georgia-company-formation" style="display:block;text-decoration:none">
          <span class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:14px">Georgia</span>
          <h3>Georgia</h3>
          <p>The Estonian model — 15% on distributed profit only — plus the Virtual Zone for IT.</p>
          <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold)">Read →</span>
        </a>
        <a class="card reveal reveal-delay-2" href="/insights/belgium-company-formation" style="display:block;text-decoration:none">
          <span class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:14px">Belgium</span>
          <h3>Belgium</h3>
          <p>The BV/SRL, 25% / 20% SME corporate tax, 21% VAT and the holding &amp; IP regimes.</p>
          <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold)">Read →</span>
        </a>
        <a class="card reveal" href="/insights/switzerland-company-formation" style="display:block;text-decoration:none">
          <span class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:14px">Switzerland</span>
          <h3>Switzerland</h3>
          <p>GmbH vs AG, the three-tier tax (~12–21% by canton), 8.1% VAT and the participation exemption.</p>
          <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold)">Read →</span>
        </a>
        <a class="card reveal reveal-delay-1" href="/insights/saudi-arabia-company-formation" style="display:block;text-decoration:none">
          <span class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:14px">Saudi Arabia</span>
          <h3>Saudi Arabia</h3>
          <p>MISA licensing, the 20% tax / 2.5% Zakat split, 15% VAT and the 30-year RHQ incentive.</p>
          <span style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold)">Read →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2 class="reveal">Ready to Begin?</h2>
    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1">If you have a specific question about operating in a jurisdiction we cover, the fastest route to an answer is a direct conversation with a senior ARM advisor.</p>
    <div class="btn-row reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Schedule a Consultation →</a>
      <a href="/" class="btn-secondary">Return Home</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>
</Base>
